    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em>In the shadowy land of Nidal, the influence of Zon-Kuthon and the Midnight Lord’s favored servants—the kytons— taints the land and its inhabitants. Just as an eclipse drives animals wild, so too does the darkness unleash a madness from deep within you.</em><br><br><strong>Bonus Feats:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>@Compendium[pf1.feats.Q1cY8r0Pvb66pMG0]{Alertness}</li>\n<li>@Compendium[pf1.feats.pmAO1Sni8xx71pLF]{Blind-Fight}</li>\n<li>@Compendium[pf1.feats.BJBC4lbo7xGWPsKJ]{Exotic Weapon Proficiency} (spiked chain),</li>\n<li>@Compendium[pf1.feats.fVRnBIHR4Jq6btvm]{Great Fortitude}</li>\n<li>Improved Dirty Trick,</li>\n<li>@Compendium[pf1.feats.iAbIGhm7T2OK9Brt]{Iron Will}</li>\n<li>@Compendium[pf1.feats.8snLqsJN4LLL00Nq]{Toughness}</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Bonus Spells:&nbsp;</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>@Compendium[pf1.spells.ijtqp1h3hka5kive]{Persuasive Goad} (7th),&nbsp;</li>\n<li>@Compendium[pf1.spells.jy64xofud29j5ju6]{Pain Strike} (10th),&nbsp;</li>\n<li>@Compendium[pf1.spells.jdsvncnna6oy189a]{Deeper Darkness} (13th),</li>\n<li>@Compendium[pf1.spells.be88e90guqbi1q1z]{Fear} (16th)</li>\n</ul>",
